    <item>
      <title>美国批准向以色列出售价值 188 亿美元的战斗机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/us-approves-sale-of-fighter-jets-to-israel-in-18-8-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府批准向以色列出售多达 50 架 F-15 战斗机、车辆和弹药，价值超过 200 亿美元，这明确表明，尽管人们对以色列军队在加沙的战争行为感到担忧，但武器仍将继续流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/us-approves-sale-of-fighter-jets-to-israel-in-18-8-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 20:15:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球移民打击行动使留学生陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/global-immigration-crackdown-ensnares-students-studying-abroad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际学生 — — 长期以来一直是发达经济体高校的摇钱树 — — 面临着越来越不确定的未来，因为各国政府都在寻求简单的目标来控制激增的移民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/global-immigration-crackdown-ensnares-students-studying-abroad</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
